### **4. 23_LiveStreamScope**  
**Description:**  
Plots incoming numeric data as a smooth, real-time line chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveStreamScope - Real-Time Chart Visualizer

LiveStreamScope renders incoming metric streams into a scrolling chart, great for dashboards and monitoring.

## Features
- Realtime updates  
- Matplotlib chart rendering  
- Adjustable refresh rate  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_LiveStreamScope.git
cd 23_LiveStreamScope
python visualize.py
